      "front": "What is the kernel of an operating system?",
      "back": "The kernel is the central part of an operating system that manages computer hardware and provides services to applications."
    },
    {
      "front": "What is the role of the device driver in an operating system?",
      "back": "The device driver is a system component that interacts with a hardware device and translates operating system requests into commands that the device can understand."
